ingredients:
    batter:
        - rice (pachari)
        - urad dal (uzhunnu)
        - boiled keral rice (optional)
        - salt (as per requirement)
    batter ingredients ratio:
        - 4:1:0.75(0.5-0.75) 
process:
    - add rice, urad dal and boiled rice to the mixer
    - mix it using mixer until no tharitharip - more soft if more powdered it is
    - add salt as per your preference and mix it well
    - since batter fermentation makes the batter doubled or tripled, transfer the batter into a big container
    - keep it for fermentation for 12 hours
    - after 12 hours, mix it well (batter will come down then)
    - make dosha
